{"talk":{"id":2512,"name":"Joseph Ravenell: How barbershops can keep men healthy","description":"The barbershop can be a safe haven for black men, a place for honest conversation and trust -- and, as physician Joseph Ravenell suggests, a good place to bring up tough topics about health. He's turning the barbershop into a place to talk about medical problems that statistically affect black men more often and more seriously, like high blood pressure. It's a new approach to problem solving with broad applications. \"What is your barbershop?\" he asks. \"Where is that place for you where people affected by a unique problem can meet a unique solution?\"","slug":"joseph_ravenell_how_barbershops_can_keep_men_healthy","recorded_at":"2016-02-16 00:00:00","published_at":"2016-05-26 15:06:43","updated_at":"2021-04-09 19:45:34","viewed_count":1127376,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":377,"name":"TED2016"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/bf1562565f2ae6acebe827e151b196dca1b35eef_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/bf1562565f2ae6acebe827e151b196dca1b35eef_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/bf1562565f2ae6acebe827e151b196dca1b35eef_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/bf1562565f2ae6acebe827e151b196dca1b35eef_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/6094382cb03573581a6b2e3f6c7f0ce1adf7173c_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/JosephRavenell_2016-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":6520842,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/JosephRavenell_2016-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":18036910,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/JosephRavenell_2016-320k.mp4?apike